OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mainly dry and settled day
OL,6,Fwith some brightness at first, but
OL,7,Fwith more cloud tending to develop
OL,8,Fthrough the day. Feeling cooler
OL,9,Fcompared to Monday, especially around
OL,10,Fcoasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA mainly dry but rather
OL,13,Fcloudy evening and night, with just
OL,14,Fthe odd spot of light rain or drizzle
OL,15,Fpossible at first.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
