OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA dry but fairly cloudy
OL,6,Fmorning. Cloud will partly break up
OL,7,Fthrough the afternoon, allowing some
OL,8,Fbright or sunny spells to develop,
OL,9,Fespecially across northern
OL,10,FAberdeenshire and Moray.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,13,Fand warm on Thursday with sunny
OL,14,Fspells, but cloudier, cooler east
OL,15,Fcoast at times. Variable cloud with
OL,16,Frisk of a few showers on Friday and
OL,17,FSaturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
